Notes:
Season opener for both teams...UWO wins season opener for the 33rd time in 42
years...UWO makes 10 3-point baskets...UWO gets 13 points and 8 rebounds from
Samuels...EC's Pope has a game-high 19 points...EC's Jiran has 10 points and
11 rebounds...UWO built 25-5 lead before EC cut deficit to 31-21.
Game.Officials: Mark Andrews,  Duane Ives,  Mark Woelfel
